.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmqg90hj8_vedanta_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20industrial%20incident%20show%20process%20water%20lake%20downstream%20of%20a%20pond%20that%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20formed%20by%20'red%20mud'.%20A%20large%20volume%20of%20muddy%20red%20water%20was%20also%20seen%20flowing%20into%20open%20areas.%20The%20water%20covered%20the%20ground%20where%20some%20trees%20stood%2C%20and%20ran%20over%20other%20forms%20of%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fvvdnu83_vedanta_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20'red%20mud'%20has%20been%20handled%20in%20slurry%20form%20and%20stored%20in%20ponds%20that%20have%20caused%20adverse%20impacts%20on%20the%20environment%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20the%20CPCB%20says%20in%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20injuries%20or%20loss%20of%20livestock%20due%20to%20the%20flooding%20caused%20by%20the%20breach%2C%20a%20Vedanta%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpvnpmni8_vedanta_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20disruption%20in%20our%20current%20operations%20and%20the%20refinery%20continues%20to%20operate%20in%20compliance%20with%20regulatory%20requirements.%20Additionally%2C%20t