as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Nathan%20Marx%2C%20a%20deckhand%20for%20a%20superyacht.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202020%20to%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20I%20was%20a%20quality%20controller%20at%20an%20engineering%20company%20that%20made%20mining%20machinery%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20I%20managed%20132%20employees%20and%20earned%203%2C000%20euros%2C%20around%20%243%2C333%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20future%20was%20pretty%20secure%20at%20the%20company%2C%20but%20I%20lacked%20that%20sense%20of%20adventure%20and%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20more%20to%20life%20than%20working%20away%20every%20day%20and%20not%20seeing%20the%20world%20as%20I%20would%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20some%20friends%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20yachting%20industry%20since%20leaving%20school%2C%20and%20it%20looked%20very%20intriguing%20and%20adventurous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20previous%20job%20had%20long%20hours%20and%20was%20hard%20work%2C%20which%20made%20me%20comfortable%20stepping%20into%20the%20yachting%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20working%20on%20deckhand%20certification%20courses%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20I%20was%20told%20about%20these%20massive%20yachting%20hubs%20where%20it'd%20be%20easier%20to%20find%20work%20opportunities%20because%20they%20were%20saturated%20with%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20was%20Antibes%2C%20France.%20I%20moved%20there%20in%20May%20this%20year%20and%20traveled%20the%20entire%20coastline%20of%20the%20south%20of%20France%2C%20dock%20walking%20daily%2C%20exploring%20the%20vessels%2C%20and%20putting%20myself%20out%20there%20to%20catch%20the%20right%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20documenting%20my%20job%20search%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40nathmarx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20day%20I%20left%20for%20France.%20I%20was%20very%20nervous%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20job%20yet%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20stand%20out%20and%20get%20a%20step%20ahead%20in%20my%20job%20search.%20I%20love%20expressing%20myself%20through%20video%20creation%2C%20so%20the%20two%20went%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20this%20girl%20who%20works%20on%20this%20vessel%20docked%20in%20Monaco%20for%20the%20season.%20She%20saw%20my%20videos%2C%20and%20we%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other.%20I%20was%20the%20first%20person%20she%20contacted%20when%20they%20needed%20a%20deckhand.%20So%20it's%20all%20about%20getting%20in%20front%20of%20the%20right%20people's%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20role%20on%20the%20yacht%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20boat's%20exterior%20is%20pristine.%20Everything%20regarding%20the%20exterior%2C%20from%20the%20hull%20to%20the%20deck%2C%20to%20any%20furniture%20outside%2C%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20presentable%20for%20guests.%20I%20also%20help%20with%20basic%20watchkeeping%20when%20the%20yacht%20is%20out%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20three%20months%20in%2C%20I'm%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20food%20chain%20and%20I'm%20earning%201%2C000%20euros%20less%20every%20month%20than%20I%20did%20back%20in%20South%20Africa.%20But%20this%20career%20has%20room%20for%20growth%20and%20will%20keep%20me%20above%20the%20ceiling%20that%20I%20reached%20in%20South%20Africa%20in%20my%20management%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20realized%20working%20on%20yachts%20is%20that%20you%20live%20in%20the%20same%20space%20as%20your%20coworkers.%20If%20something%20bothers%20you%20about%20a%20person%20and%20you%20keep%20quiet%2C%20it%20builds%20within%20you%20and%20just%20sours%20the%20relationship%20on%20board.%20You%20have%20to%20foster%20a%20relationship%20with%20them%20that%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20fruitful%20than%20a%20normal%20employee%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20also%20value%20that%20because%20not%20only%20am%20I%20getting%20to%20travel%20or%20experience%20all%20these%20crazy%20things%20that%20normal%20people%20in%20a%209-to-5%20usually%20won't%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20meeting%20people%20and%20creating%20connections%20with%20them%20that'll%20last%20a%20lifetime%20instead.%20That%20real%20connection%20with%20people%20also%20gives%20me%20satisfaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20life%20outside%20this%20industry%20might%20be%20challenging%20because%20anything%20can%20happen%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20You%20might%20have%20time%20to%20spare%20one%20moment%2C%20but%20you're%20expecting%20guests%20the%20next%2C%20and%20you're%20suddenly%20back%20to%20work%20for%20a%20week.%20So%20whatever%20you%20have%20planned%20just%20needs%20to%20fall%20on%20the%20back%20burner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20maritime%20industry%20here%20sets%20out%20work-life%20balance%20very%20well%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20yachting%20industry%20because%20my%20previous%20job%20did%20not%20value%20my%20personal%20life.%20So%2C%20after%20the%20hard%20work%2C%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20off%20time%2C%20and%20I%20have%20time%20to%20go%20and%20experience%20things%20and%20step%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20places%20I%20visited%20was%20Corsica%2C%20France%2C%20a%20beautiful%20little%20town%20on%20a%20hill%20with%20an%20absurd%20history.%20We%20also%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20hiking%20up%20into%20the%20old%20city%2C%20an%20amazing%20experience%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20would've%20had%20otherwise%20if%20I%20wasn't%20into%20the%20yachting%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221918%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nathan%20Marx%20Corsica%20France%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e11fc983b8099cf9fd6b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20Corsica%2C%20France%2C%20from%20Marx's%20time%20in%20the%20town.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Marx%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20once%20spoke%20to%20a%20person%20who's%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20around%20nine%20years.%20He%20told%20me%20about%20chartering%20Will%20Smith%20and%20all%20these%20big%20A-list%20star%20names%2C%20which%20sounded%20so%20enticing.%20I%20haven't%20had%20any%20of%20those%20or%20any%20experiences%20like%20that%2C%20but%20the%20individuals%20we%20meet%20on%20this%20boat%20are%20very%20high-net-worth%20because%20renting%20the%20vessel%20I%20work%20on%20costs%20about%2078%2C000%20euros%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20once%20had%20a%20client%20with%203.2%20million%20Instagram%20followers%20on%20board%20and%20had%20a%20normal%20conversation%20with%20her.%20It%20was%20humbling%20to%20me%20because%20you%20always%20think%20these%20people%20will%20be%20different%20or%20special%20in%20some%20way%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20they're%20just%20normal%20people.%20She%20never%20mentioned%20anything%20about%20her%20success%20once.%20It%20was%20so%20normal%20that%20I%20was%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20motivating%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20individuals%20like%20that%20because%20they%20make%20you%20feel%20that%20their%20success%20is%20possible%20for%20you%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20superyacht%20industry%20is%20unlike%20other%20luxury%20sectors.%20The%20places%20people%20visit%20are%20so%20unique%20that%20not%20everyone%20gets%20to%20see%20them.%20The%20cost%20involved%20is%20also%20quite%20exorbitant%2C%20with%20some%20yachts%20going%20for%20500%2C000%20euros%20a%20week.%20So%2C%20the%20client%20has%20a%20level%20of%20expectation%20of%20luxury%20they%20want%20to%20receive%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20live%20up%20to%20very%20high%20standards%20that%20no%20other%20luxury%20industry%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20career%20can%20progress%20from%20here%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20and%20I'm%20trying%20to%20explore%20all%20those%20avenues.%20But%20the%20yachting%20industry%20is%20a%20tight-knit%20community%20that's%20made%20me%20very%20happy%20over%20the%20past%20few%20mon