sion-making%20closer%20to%20the%20front%20lines%20where%20it%20most%20impacts%20customers%20(and%20the%20business)%2C%20decreases%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20strengthen%20our%20organizations'%20ability%20to%20make%20customers'%20lives%20better%20and%20easier%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ2.%20Why%20are%20we%20taking%20these%20steps%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20have%20grown%20our%20teams%20quickly%20and%20substantially%2C%20we%20have%20understandably%20added%20a%20lot%20of%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20process%2C%20we%20have%20also%20added%20more%20layers%20than%20we%20had%20before.%20It's%20created%20artifacts%20that%20we'd%20like%20to%20change%20(e.g.%2C%20pre-meetings%20for%20the%20pre-meetings%20for%20the%20decision%20meetings%2C%20a%20longer%20line%20of%20managers%20feeling%20like%20they%20need%20to%20review%20a%20topic%20before%20it%20moves%20forward%2C%20owners%20of%20initiatives%20feeling%20less%20like%20they%20should%20make%20recommendations%20because%20the%20decision%20will%20be%20made%20elsewhere%2C%20etc.).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20more%20of%20our%20teammates%20feeling%20like%20they%20can%20move%20fast%20without%20unnecessary%20processes%2C%20meetings%2C%20mechanisms%2C%20and%20layers%20that%20create%20overhead%20and%20waste%20valuable%20time.%20We%20believe%20now%20is%20the%20right%20time%20to%20bring%20us%20all%20closer%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20reinforce%20our%20culture%20of%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ3.%20What%20is%20the%20timeline%20for%20when%20orgs%20will%20make%20this%20shift%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20senior%20leaders%20across%20Amazon%20will%20be%20examining%20their%20organizations%20for%20opportunities%20to%20advance%20an%20even%20more%20customer-centric%20team%20structure%20that%20fosters%20agility%20and%20empowers%20frontline%20decision%20making.%20This%20is%20long-term%2C%20iterative%20work%2C%20but%20we%20believe%20most%20orgs%20will%20