nuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20decided%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20return%20to%20being%20in%20the%20office%20the%20way%20we%20were%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20COVID%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20advantages%20of%20being%20together%20in%20the%20office%20are%20significant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employees%20disagreed%20with%20that%20premise%2C%20while%20others%20criticized%20the%20move%20on%20other%20grounds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20%26quot%3BFrequently%20Asked%20Questions%26quot%3B%20document%20shared%20with%20employees%20describes%20how%20the%20new%20RTO%20policy%20will%20work.%20Business%20Insider%20obtained%20a%20copy.%20Amazon%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20bottom%20of%20the%2022-question%20document%2C%20Amazon%20withdrew%20another%20remote-work%20benefit.%20It%20has%20ended%20a%20policy%20that%20gave%3Cspan%3E%20employees%20the%20option%20to%20work%20up%20to%20four%20weeks%20per%20year%20fully%20remote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20all%20the%20details%20from%20the%20FAQ%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ1.%20How%20often%20are%20corporate%20employees%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20going%20to%20return%20to%20being%20in%20the%20office%20the%20way%20we%20were%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20When%20we%20look%20back%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20advantages%20of%20being%20together%20in%20the%20office%20are%20significant.%20This%20means%20the%20general%20expectation%20is%20that%20if%20you%20are%20working%20during%20the%20week%2C%20you%20are%20doing%20so%20from%20the%20office.%20We%20recognize%20there%20will%20occasionally%20be%20days%20when%20someone%20might%20need%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20the%20day%20(e.g.%2C%20you%20or%20your%20child%20are%20sick%2C%20you%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20house%20emergency%2C%20or%20you%20need%20a%20day%20or%20two%20to%20finish%20coding%20in%20a%20more%20isolated%20environment)%2C%20and%20for%20those%20occasions%2C%20employees%20should%20proactively%20communicate%20with%20their%20manager%2C%20just%20as%20they%20would%20have%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ2.%20I%20joined%20Amazon%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20What%20does%20%26quot%3Bworking%20like%20we%20did%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic%26quot%3B%20mean%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20all%20worked%20together%20in%20the%20office.%20Employees%20and%20managers%20proactively%20communicated%20with%20one%20another%20about%20their%20whereabouts%2C%20and%20when%20an%20employee%20needed%20flexibility%2C%20they%20discussed%20it%20with%20their%20manager%20and%20worked%20it%20out.%20There%20was%20flexibility%20when%20you%20needed%20it%2C%20but%20a%20general%20expectation%20and%20practice%20of%20being%20in%20the%20office%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ3.%20When%20will%20we%20begin%20working%20this%20way%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20teams%20are%20already%20working%20this%20way%2C%20and%20we%20encourage%20Amazonians%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20person%20together%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20can.%20We%20also%20recognize%20it%20might%20take%20some%20time%20for%20people%20to%20adjust%2C%20so%20we%20expect%20teams%20to%20begin%20fully%20working%20this%20way%20by%20January%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ4.%20With%20this%20update%2C%20will%20I%20have%20an%20assigned%20workspace%2Fdesk%20in%20the%20office%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20locations%20organized%20with%20an%20assigned%20workspace%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20including%20U.S.%20headquarters%20locations%20(Puget%20Sound%20and%20Arlington)%2C%20assigned%20desk%20arrangements%20will%20be%20available.%20For%20locations%20that%20had%20agile%20desk%20arrangements%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20including%20much%20of%20Europe%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20operate%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ5.%20How%20long%20will%20it%20take%20to%20have%20an%20assigned%20workspace%2Fdesk%20if%20I%20am%20in%20a%20location%20that%20had%20one%20before%20the%20pandemic%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20employees%2C%20assigned%20workspaces%20will%20be%20available%20by%20January%202%2C%202025.%20We%20will%20post%20an%20update%20from%20Global%20Real%20Estate%20and%20Facilities%20(GREF)%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%20with%20more%20specifics%20on%20timing%20for%20our%20various%20office%20locations.%20If%20your%20assigned%20workspace%20isn't%20ready%20by%20January%202%2C%20we%20still%20expect%20everyone%20to%20begin%20fully%20working%20from%20the%20office%20by%20that%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ6.%20Why%20will%20we%20still%20have%20agile%20seating%20in%20some%20locations%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20teams%20prefer%20agile%20seating%20because%20it%20provides%20a%20flexible%20and%20collaborative%20work%20environment%20that%20is%20designed%20around%20the%20concept%20of%20team%20neighborhoods%20that%20balance%20individual%20workspace%20with%20team%20collaboration.%20These%20agile%20workplaces%20have%20unassigned%20seating%20that%20is%20allocated%20to%20specific%20teams%2C%20allowing%20employees%20to%20move%20freely%20within%20their%20neighborhood%20as%20they%20shift%20between%20different%20work%20activities.%20Many%20teams%20prefer%20this%20agile%20arrangement%20with%20neighborhoods%20and%20have%20chosen%20to%20work%20this%20way%2C%20both%20before%20the%20pandemic%20and%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ7.%20Will%20we%20continue%20to%20have%20badging%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20but%20our%20hope%20is%20that%20over%20time%20this%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20necessary.%20Continuing%20to%20report%20badge%20data%20for%20now%20will%20help%20us%20track%20our%20progress%20and%20support%20conversations%20between%20employees%20and%20their%20managers%20as%20we%20go%20through%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ8.%20How%20will%20badge%20reporting%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20badge%20reports%20provide%20visibility%20of%20the%20days%20you%20badged%20into%20an%20Amazon%20building.%20This%20includes%20nearly%20all%20corporate%20buildings%2C%20data%20centers%2C%20fulfillment%20centers%2C%20and%20delivery%20stations.%20The%20badge%20reporting%20system%20will%20also%20reflect%20any%20PTO%20which%20you've%20recorded%2C%20including%20recorded%20sick%20days%20and%20leaves%20of%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ9.%20Does%20the%20badge%20report%20account%20for%20days%20when%20I'm%20traveling%20for%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20not%20reflect%20when%20you're%20traveling%20for%20business%20(e.g.%2C%20the%20days%20you%20don't%20badge%20into%20an%20Amazon%20building)%2C%20or%20when%20you're%20at%20an%20external%20conference%20or%20customer%20site.%20For%20these%20occasions%2C%20you%20should%20just%20let%20your%20manager%20know%20your%20whereabouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ10.%20If%20there's%20a%20day%20when%20I%20will%20not%20be%20working%20in%20the%20office%2C%20that's%20not%20covered%20by%20PTO%2C%20what%20do%20I%20need%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recognize%20there%20will%20occasionally%20be%20days%20when%20someone%20might%20need%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20from%20home%20(e.g.%2C%20you%20or%20your%20child%20are%20sick%2C%20you%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20house%20emergency%2C%20or%20you%20need%20a%20day%20or%20two%20to%20finish%20coding%20in%20a%20more%20isolated%20environment)%2C%20and%20for%20those%20occasions%2C%20employees%20should%20simply%20discuss%20with%20their%20manager%20and%20let%20them%20know%20why%20they%20need%20to%20work%20from%20home%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ11.%20What%20if%20I'm%20not%20feeling%20well%2C%20am%20I%20still%20expected%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20sick%2C%20you%20should%20stay%20home%20until%20you're%20better.%20Sick%20leave%20and%20other%20absences%20should%20be%20reported%20through%20your%20normal%20reporting%20process.%20If%20you're%20starting%20to%20feel%20well%20enough%20to%20work%20but%20concerned%20about%20getting%20your%20teammates%20sick%2C%20talk%20to%20your%20manager%20about%20working%20from%20home%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ12.%20What%20if%20I'm%20trying%20to%20do%20all%20the%20right%20things%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20weeks%20that%20I'm%20just%20not%20able%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%20each%20day%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20appreciate%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20employees%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20following%20the%20intent%20of%20these%20expectations%20and%20regularly%20communicating%20with%20their%20manager%20about%20any%20extenuating%20circumstances.%20As%20we%20always%20do%2C%20we'll%20have%20direct%20conversations%20with%20employees%20who%20are%20not%20meeting%20expectations%20to%20ensure%20they%20have%20what%20they%20need%20and%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ13.%20I'm%20the%20only%20or%20one%20of%20just%20a%20few%20people%20from%20my%20team%20in%20the%20office%20I'm%20assigned%20to%20does%20this%20update%20apply%20to%20me%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20We%20believe%20that%20employees%20are%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20understand%20our%20unique%20culture%20and%20become%20part%20of%20it%20if%20they're%20surrounded%20by%20other%20Amazonians%20in%20person%2C%20even%20if%20not%20on%20their%20immediate%20working%20team.%20We%20also%20encourage%20managers%20to%20work%20towards%20having%20as%20many%20of%20their%20team%20members%20together%20In%20one%20physical%20location%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ14.%20If%20I%20currently%20have%20an%20approved%20exception%20(e.g.%2C%20Field%20by%20Design%20or%20Virtual)%20does%20this%20update%20change%20where%20I%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20this%20update%20does%20not%20impact%20employees%20who%20are%20in%20roles%20that%20are%20Field%20by%20Design%2C%20Virtual%2C%20or%20have%20a%20Remote%20Work%20Exception%20or%20Military%20Spouse%20Remote%20Work%20Exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ15.%20How%20do%20I%20request%20an%20exception%20to%20work%20remotely%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInformation%20on%20how%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20Remote%20Work%20Exception%20is%20available%20on%20A%20to%20Z%2C%20and%20s-team%20member%20approval%20is%20required%20for%20remote%20work%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ16.%20What%20commuting%20benefits%20does%20Amazon%20offer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20provides%20a%20variety%20of%20commuter%20benefits%20and%20services%20to%20give%20employees%20flexibility%20for%20their%20commute%20to%20the%20office.%20Available%20benefits%20and%20subsidies%20vary%20by%20site%2C%20even%20within%20the%20same%20country.%3Cbr%3EU.S.-based%20employees%20can%20set%20up%20and%20log%20into%20their%20MyCommute%20account%20to%20find%20out%20more%20about%20their%20available%20commuter%20benefits%20and%20services.%20Employees%20in%20Americas-based%20sites%20outside%20of%20the%20U.S.%2C%20EMEA%2C%20and%20APAC%20can%20visit%20the%20Global%20Benefit's%20page%20to%20view%20commuter%20benefits%20for%20your%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ17.%20What%20are%20my%20options%20for%20commuting%20to%20the%20office%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20continue%20to%20support%20diverse%20ways%20of%20commuting%20to%20the%20office%2C%20including%20ways%20that%20minimize%20reliance%20on%20single-occupancy%20vehicles%20in%20line%20with%20our%20sustainability%20goals.%20Commute%20options%20vary%20by%20location-visit%20GREF%20commute%20to%20find%20specific%20options%20available%20for%20your%20location.%20Public%20transit%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20best%20option%20for%20many%20and%20we%20encourage%20this%20as%20a%20first%20option.%20Where%20we%20currently%20have%20shuttle%20services%20and%2For%20ride-sharing%2C%20we%20are%20increasing%20frequency%20of%20existing%20routes%20and%20increasing%20capacity%20with%20more%20routes.%20We%20will%20also%20be%20adding%20ride%20sharing%20in%20some%20new%20locations%20where%20other%20options%20are%20not%20meeting%20demand.%20Bicycle%20and%20similar%20e-powered%20modes%20continue%20to%20be%20an%20option.%20Where%20we%20have%20parking%20facilities%2C%20employees%20may%20opt%20to%20carpool%20or%20drive%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ18.%20What%20is%20GREF%20doing%20to%20increase%20meeting%20room%20availability%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20existing%20locations%2C%20GREF%20is%20working%20with%20IT%20Services%20to%20improve%20our%20booking%20technology%20and%20utilization%20habits%20which%20will%20increase%20capacity%20of%20existing%20meeting%20rooms%20by%2075%2C000%20hours%2Fmonth%20globally%2C%20focusing%20on%20locations%20where%20meeting%20rooms%20are%20currently%20exceeding%2050%25%20average%20daily%20utilization.%20This%20includes%20removal%20of%20false%20bookings%2C%20a%20required%20check-in%20and%20check-out%20tool%2C%20and%20communications%20on%20appropriate%20meeting%20room%20booking%20to%20ensure%20efficient%20use%20of%20rooms%20given%20the%20meeting%20size.%20We%20will%20install%20additional%20phone%20booths%20where%20they%20are%20now%20inadequate%20and%20where%20space%20allows%20starting%20in%20September%2C%20continuing%20to%20ramp%20through%20next%20year%20for%20an%20estimated%20increase%20of%20approximately%203%2C500%20globally.%20Ongoing%2C%20new%20workplaces%20will%20have%20an%20increased%20number%20of%20more%20diverse%20meeting%20rooms%20to%20meet%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ19.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20disability%20that%20requires%20an%20accommodation%20related%20to%20being%20in%20the%20office%20every%20day%2C%20how%20can%20I%20get%20support%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20employees%20with%20disabilities%20to%20identify%20the%20workplace%20accommodations%2Fadjustments%20they%20need.%20You%20can%20use%20self-service%20features%2024%2F7%20to%20submit%20a%20request%20to%20Disability%20%26amp%3B%20Leave%20Services%20if%20you%20have%20a%20medical%20condition%20or%20disability%20is%20impacting%20your%20ability%20to%20perform%20the%20functions%20of%20your%20role.%20Access%20My%20HR%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20medical%20accommodation.%20You%20can%20also%20start%20a%20live%20chat%20or%20phone%20call%20via%20My%20HR%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20what%20options%20are%20available%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ20.%20If%20I'm%20a%20nursing%20parent%2C%20what%20accommodations%20are%20available%20in%20the%20office%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20provides%20accommodation%20for%20employees%20who%20wish%20to%20express%20and%20store%20breast%20milk.%20Visit%20the%20Global%20Lactation%20Accommodation%20page%20on%20Inside%20Amazon%20for%20policy%20details%20and%20reach%20out%20to%20My_HR%20if%20you%20have%20any%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ21.%20What%20benefits%20or%20resources%20do%20we%20have%20to%20support%20child%2C%20pet%2C%20and%20elder%20care%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20applicable%2C%20Amazon%20provides%20access%20to%20elder%20care%20options%20and%20pet%20sitters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20free%20memberships%20to%20online%20referral%20services%20where%20you%20can%20find%20trusted%20caregivers.%20Learn%20more%20by%20visiting%20the%20Benefits%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ22.%20With%20this%20update%2C%20will%20we%20continue%20to%20have%20the%20option%20to%20work%20four%20weeks%20out%20of%20the%20year%20from%20anywhere%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20Moving%20forward%2C%20when%20an%20employee%20needs%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20from%20a%20location%20outside%20of%20their%20assigned%20offic