y%20a%20pilot%20police%20vehicle%2C%20around%2030%20doctors%20had%20arrived%20at%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20home%20at%206.20%20pm.%20The%20meeting%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20begin%C2%A0%20at%205%20pm%2C%20finally%20started%20around%207%20pm%20and%20ended%20around%209%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%2C%20though%2C%20are%20yet%20to%20emerge%20from%20the%20Chief%20Ministers'%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20earlier%20meetings%20--%20the%20last%20one%20attempted%20on%20Saturday%20--%20had%20fallen%20though%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20could%20not%20come%20to%20a%20consensus%20on%20whether%20the%20proceedings%20should%20be%20live%20transmitted%20or%20videographed%2C%20with%20the%20video%20handed%20to%20the%20doctors%20right%20after%20it%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20reached%20the%20venue%20but%20left%20without%20sitting%20down%20at%20the%20proverbial%20table.%20On%20the%20first%20occasion%2C%20images%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20sitting%20in%20an%20empty%20meeting%20hall%20of%20the%20state%20secretariat%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20doctors'%20delegation%2C%20had%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20did%20Saturday's%20cellphone%20videos%20of%20her%20asking%20the%20doctors%20to%20come%20inside%20her%20Kalighat%20home%20and%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20at%20least%20even%20if%20they%20were%20unwilling%20to%20join%20discussions.%20The%20doctors%20had%20refused%2C%20saying%20they%20want%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20most%20of%20the%20conditions%20have%20been%20laid%20down%20in%20writing%20ahead%20of%20the%20meet%2C%20negating%20any%20chance%20of%20last-minute%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20taken%20their%20own%20stenographers%20who%20would%20record%20the%20minutes%20and%20the%20document%20will%20be%20signed%20by%20everyone%20present.%20The%20government%20will%20also%20have%20a%20video%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20also%20stipulated%20that%20they%20give%20their%20response%20to%20whatever%20the%20government%20had%20to%20say%20after%20going%20back%20to%20the%20protest%20site%20and%20discussing%20it%20with%20the%20others.%20They%20have%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20will%20not%20give%20up%20on%20their%20five-point%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20want%20the%20issue%20to%20be%20resolved%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20any%20form%20of%20compromise%20on%20our%20five%20demands.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20the%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20all%20the%20issues%20with%20an%20open%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20protesters%20who%20is%20also%20participating%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impasse%20over%20the%20doctors'%20demand%20for%20justice%20for%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20medic%20has%20been%20on%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ordered%20that%20the%20doctors%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20ceasework%20and%20get%20back%20to%20patient%20care%2C%20which%20is%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20had%20ended%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20ceasework%2C%20as%20doctors%20across%20India%20had%20stood%20up%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20the%20protesters.%20But%20Bengal%20doctors%20had%20refused%2C%20doubling%20down%20with%20the%20protests%20as%20the%20common%20people%20kept%20up%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20first%20time%20the%20talks%20fell%20through%20even%20before%20they%20started%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%C2%A0%20had%20assured%20doctors%20that%20no%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%20and%20that%20the%20government%20is%20always%20ready%20for%20a%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%2C%20she%20said%2C%20had%20taken%20action%20in%20similar%20circumstances.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20have%20ESMA%20(Essential%20Services%20Maintenance%20Act).%20But%20I%20will%20not%20do