%20Chhattisgarh%20Government%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20concerning%20development%2C%20the%20largest%20government%20hospital%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20stopped%20open-heart%20surgeries%20for%20four%20months%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20reagents.%20This%20has%20left%20many%20economically%20weaker%20patients%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Dr%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20Hospital%20in%20huge%20trouble%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20seek%20expensive%20private%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReagents%2C%20which%20are%20used%20in%20tests%20before%20and%20during%20the%20surgery%2C%20are%20in%20short%20supply%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Raipur%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impoverished%20states%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20who%20depend%20on%20government%20healthcare%20are%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20this%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadan%20Gopal%2C%20a%20security%20guard%20from%20Korba%20district%2C%20has%20been%20running%20from%20one%20hospital%20to%20another%20for%20his%20surgery.%20His%20family%20eventually%20took%20loans%20to%20treat%20him%20at%20a%20private%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20referred%20to%20Raipur%20AIIMS%2C%20and%20then%20further%20referred%20to%20Ambedkar%20Hospital.%20But%20we%20were%20told%20that%20surgeries%20are%20on%20hold%20there.%20After%20another%20visit%20to%20AIIMS%2C%20we%20were%20told%20the%20waiting%20period%20was%20too%20long%20for%20my%20father's%20condition%2C%20so%20we%20are%20now%20struggling%20to%20arrange%20funds%20for%20private%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gopal's%20son%20Ankush%20Kumar%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospital%20performs%2030-40%20heart%20surgeries%20a%20month%2C%20but%20the%20shortage%20of%20reagents%20in%20the%20advanced%20cardiac%20department%20has%20been%20crippling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20the%20reagent%2C%20the%20heart-lung%20machine%2C%20which%20keeps%20the%20patient%20alive%20during%20the%20procedure%2C%20cannot%20be%20properly%20monitored%2C%20and%20the%20patient%20might%20not%20survive%20the%20surgery%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20KK%20Sahu%2C%20head%20of%20department%20of%20advanced%20cardiac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20said%20the%20situation%20will%20be%20resolved%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20necessary%20equipment%20has%20been%20approved%20for%20purchase.%20The%20old%20system%20is%20being%20replaced.%20The%20dean%20will%20be%20authorised%20to%20buy%20equipment%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%2C%20with%20emergency%20purchases%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20Health%20Minister%20Shyam%20Bihari%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20claims%20to%20provide%20better%20healthcare%20in%20public%20hospitals%2C%20the%20halt%20of%20surgeries%20at%20Ambedkar%20Hospital%20due%20to%20reagent%20shortages%20raises%20serious%20concerns.%20If%20such%20disruptions%20can%20occur%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Raipur%2C%20it's%20alarming%20to%20consider%20the%20state%20of%20facilities%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20health%20experts%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726498500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcbf1ogf_ambedkar_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-reagents-open-heart-surgeries-stopped-in-chhattisgarhs-largest-government-hospital-6578325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20concerning%20development%2C%20the%20largest%20government%20hospital%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20stopped%20open-heart%20surgeries%20for%20four%20months%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20reagents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-reagents-open-heart-surgeries-stopped-in-chhattisgarhs-largest-government-hospital-6578325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Art%20Helped%20Me%20Heal%E2%80%99%3A%20Beauty%20Content%20Creator%20Mannu%E2%80%99s%20Inspiring%20Journey%20to%20Confidence%20After%20Surviving%20a%20Burn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20severe%20burns%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20this%3A%20A%20four-year-old%20and%20her%20sister%20are%20playing%20by%20the%20fireplace%3B%20the%20flames%20dancing%20to%20their%20joyful%20laughter.%20But%20in%20a%20split%20second%2C%20their%20world%20is%20turned%20upside%20down.%20Giggles%20turn%20into%20screams%20as%20the%20flames%20begin%20to%20engulf%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20was%20Manisha%20Marodia%20Prajapati%2C%20known%20on%20social%20media%20and%20by%20loved%20ones%20as%20Mannu.%20She%20survived%2C%20but%20the%20incident%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266757%2Fneehaari-mandali-burn-survivor-mission-saviour-trust-kerala-ngo-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20severe%20burns%20on%20her%20face%20and%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20would%20take%20longer%20for%20her%20emotional%20scars%20to%20heal.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20following%20years%2C%20she%20would%20etch%20an%20inspiring%20story%20of%20resilience%20and%20overcoming%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Manisha%20is%20an%20influencer%20and%20an%20artist%20with%20a%20strong%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CBeauty%20is%20not%20a%20face%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20what%20lies%20in%20your%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20recovery%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20Manisha%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Jhajjar.%20She%20underwent%20multiple%20surgeries%20to%20recover%20from%20her%20physical%20wounds%2C%20but%20the%20trauma%20lingered%20a%20little%20while%20longer.%20Her%20survival%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20due%20to%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20support.%20However%2C%20life%20outside%20