Those%20filled%20with%20hate%20are%20not%20leaving%20any%20chance%20to%20defame%20India%20and%20Gujarat...%20want%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Etukde%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Etukde%3C%2Fem%3E%20(break-up)%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20campaign%20references%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20voting%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20for%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20election%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20have%20promised%20to%20restore%20special%20status%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20under%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20was%20scrapped%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20which%20also%20split%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20two%20union%20territories%2C%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-will-never-be-restored-amit-shah-releases-bjp-manifesto-for-j-k-polls-6504854%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BArticle%20370%20Is%20History%2C%20Will%20Never%20Come%20Back%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20strike%20an%20emotive%20note%20with%20voters%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20in%20other%20poll-bound%20states%20this%20year%2C%20including%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20said%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20his%20third%20term%20had%20seen%20him%20insulted%20and%20mocked%20by%20his%20critics%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20live%20for%20you...%20I%20will%20sacrifice%20myself%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20comments%20in%20the%20US%20-%20at%20various%20public%20events%2C%20including%20those%20attended%20by%20Indian%20students%20and%20diaspora%20community%20members%20-%20have%20drawn%20fierce%20responses%20from%20a%20battery%20of%20union%20ministers%2C%20including%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20Defence%20Minister