ple%20believe%20it%2C%20some%20don't.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20apprehending%20the%20foreign%20national%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comment%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20KSO%2C%20whose%20spokesperson%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20young%20man%20who%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20called%20a%20KNA(B)%20member%20was%20indeed%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20but%20registered%20in%20the%20official%20records%20along%20with%20his%20thumb%20prints%20and%20other%20details%20as%20a%20refugee.%20The%20KSO%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20knows%20the%20man%20is%20a%20registered%20refugee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20have%20crossed%20into%20Manipur%20and%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%2C%20fleeing%20the%20conflict%20between%20pro-democracy%20ethnic%20rebels%20and%20the%20junta.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20guards%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20as%20well%20as%20conduct%20counter-insurgency%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20KSO%20general%20headquarters%20is%20shocked%20and%20surprised%20at%20the%20same%20time%20because%20someone%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20without%20inquiring%20more%20details%20about%20what's%20happening%2C%20made%20such%20a%20silly%20judgment.%20The%20apprehended%20person...%20who%20is%20from%20Myanmar%20-%20of%20course%20he%20is%20a%20foreigner%20-%20but%20has%20been%20here%20registered%20as%20a%20refugee%2C%20which%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20KSO%20spokesperson%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20all%20the%20details.%20In%20spite%20of%20all%20the%20details%20available%20on%20social%20media%20as%20well...%20when%20we%20have%20all%20these%20details%2C%20why%20would%20a%20refugee%20be%20caught%3F%20And%20then%20after%20that%20brand%20him%20a%20militant%20or%20outlaw%3F%20This%20is%20so%20wrong.%20I%20think%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20should%20be%20more%20focussed%20and%20inquire%20into%20the%20tape%20leak%20than%20any%20other%20problem%20just%20to%20deviate%20from%20what%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20leaked%20audio%20tapes%20that%20purportedly%20has%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20starting%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20tapes%20have%20been%20submitted%20to%20an%20inquiry%20panel%20under%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20and%20those%20who%20provided%20the%20tapes%20have%20given%20affidavits%20saying%20the%20content%20is%20genuine%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20by%20the%20news%20website%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20has%20called%20the%20audio%20tapes%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%2C%20meant%20to%20sabotage%20peace%20plans%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20top%20sources%20had%20told%20NDTV%20no%20KNA(B)%20member%20was%20arrested%20in%20Manipur's%20Chandel%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20some%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley.%20The%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20o