-image-67-1726490377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20teachers%2C%20says%20Nehal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20with%20kids%20below%20three%2C%20she%20says%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20go%20with%20the%20flow.%20You%20will%20experience%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20misses%20and%20hits.%20Take%20everything%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20part%20of%20the%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20some%20words%20of%20advice%20to%20parents%20in%20an%20increasingly%20competitive%20world%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20parenting%20as%20a%20pressure.%20Slow%20down.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20not%20be%20busy%20all%20the%20time.%20Let%20your%20children%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20beyond%20gadgets%20and%20video%20games.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelling%20teaches%20both%20you%20and%20your%20children%20mindfulness%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20present.%20It%20helps%20you%20shed%20your%20ego%20as%20you%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20you%20are%20not%20greater%20than%20nature.%20No%20school%20can%20provide%20the%20lessons%20that%20nature%20offers.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20fosters%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20bound%20by%20a%20shared%20love%20for%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nehal%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726491246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehal%20Shah%2C%20an%20avid%20traveller%2C%20began%20taking%20her%20son%20on%20her%20adventures%20and%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20outdoor%20experiences%20for%20families.%20Recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20nature-based%20experiences%20for%20children%2C%20she%20founded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20'stomped'%20to%20death%20in%20migrant%20boat%20crush%2C%20says%20survivor%20who%20saw%20son%20die%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726489380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-france-migrant-boat_6686232.jpg%3F20240915123805%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpeople-stomped-to-death-in-migrant-boat-crush-says-survivor-who-saw-son-die-13216201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20has%20said%20his%20son%20and%20seven%20others%20died%20after%20being%20%26quot%3Bstomped%20on%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20packed%20migrant%20boat%20as%20people%20became%20trapped%20just%20minutes%20into%20the%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpeople-stomped-to-death-in-migrant-boat-crush-says-survivor-who-saw-son-die-13216201%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Will%20Kejriwal's%20Brand%20of%20Victimhood%20Politics%20Work%20Again%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fsites%2F3%2F2019%2F10%2F04163431%2Farvind-kejriwal-banega-swasth-india.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20surprise%20announcement%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20would%20resign%20as%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20two%20days%2C%20Delhi%20Government%20ministers%20and%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leaders%20have%20been%20working%20overtime%20to%20reclaim%20the%20moral%20high%20ground%20and%20sympathy%20for%20their%20leader.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20relying%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20public%20memory%20is%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20public%20address%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court-following%20over%20five%20months%20in%20jail-Kejriwal%20argued%20that%20the%20Apex%20Court%20had%20granted%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20alleged%20cases%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20booked%20under%20the%20stringent%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20Court%20had%20given%20him%20the%20best%20possible%20relief%20and%2C%20since%20the%20trial%20and%20final%20verdict%20on%20the%20alleged%20excise%20scam%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20prolonged%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20temporarily.%20He%20stated%20he%20would%20not%20occupy%20the%20chief%20minister's%20chair%20until%20people%20certify%20his%20%26quot%3Bhonesty%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20A%20'Nightwatchman'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20is%20scheduled%20to%20begin%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20January%202025%2C%20but%20Kejriwal%20now%20wants%20the%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20November.%20In%20either%20case%2C%20Kejriwal%20aims%20to%20have%20what%20is%20known%20in%20cricketing%20terms%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnightwatchman%26quot%3B-someone%20to%20keep%20the%20position%20warm%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20AAP%20leaders%20are%20working%20to%20convince%20the%20public%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20making%20a%20significant%20sacrifice%20and%20stands%20firm%20on%20the%20moral%20front.%20Their%20main%20arguments%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKejriwal%20is%20the%20first%20politician%20to%20seek%20a%20certificate%20of%20honesty%20from%20the%20public%20in%20an%20election%3B%20voters%20should%20elect%20him%20if%20they%20believe%20he%20is%20honest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKejriwal%20is%20the%20first%20politician%20to%20resign%20after%20coming%20out%20of%20jail%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20highest%20court%2C%20and%20they%20will%20decide%20whether%20he%20is%20honest%20while%20the%20legal%20system%20evaluates%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20charges%20brought%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKejriwal%20did%20not%20resign%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20following%20his%20arrest%20on%20March%2021%2C%20because%20resigning%20would%20have%20set%20a%20precedent%20that%20could%20embolden%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20imprison%20opposition%20chief%20ministers%20and%20break%20their%20parties.%20By%20not%20resigning%2C%20Kejriwal%20thwarted%20the%20BJP's%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20examine%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20when%20Kejriwal%20says%20he%20will%20return%20as%20chief%20minister%20once%20the%20people%20give%20a%20mandate%20to%20AAP%2C%20he%20conveniently%20overlooks%20two%20crucial%20conditions%20imposed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3A%201)%20he%20cannot%20attend%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%2C%20and%202)%20he%20cannot%20sign%20off%20on%20files.%20These%20conditions%20imply%20that%20he%20cannot%20hold%20Cabinet%20meetings%20or%20engage%20in%20policy-making%20or%20policy%20reviews.%20Such%20conditions%20suggest%20that%20even%20with%20new%20elections%2C%20Kejriwal%20would%20remain%20a%20dysfunctional%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20conditions%20differ%20from%20disqualification%20cases%20like%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20office%20of%20profit%20case%2C%20where%20a%20politician%20is%20disqualified%20for%20a%20specific%20issue%20but%20may%20be%20re-elected%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20knew%20well%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20court%20order%2C%20he%20could%20have%20remained%20chief%20minister%20in%20title%20only%2C%20without%20the%20actual%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20Victory%20Isn't%20An%20Absolution%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20claim%20that%20a%20win%20in%20a%20fresh%20election%20would%20be%20a%20certificate%20of%20honesty%20from%20the%20people%20is%20dubious.%20For%20example%2C%20former%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Chautala%2C%20and%20Sukh%20Ram%20were%20re-elected%20despite%20being%20convicted%20in%20court.%20Their%20victories%20did%20not%20necessarily%20validate%20their%20honesty.%20If%20re-election%20were%20a%20true%20indicator%20of%20honesty%2C%20it%20would%20imply%20that%20almost%20no%20politician%20in%20India%20is%20corrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20should%20have%20followed%20LK%20Advani's%20example%2C%20who%2C%20when%20charged%20in%20the%20Jain%20Hawala%20case%2C%20announced%20he%20would%20not%20seek%20public%20office%20until%20he%20cleared%20his%20name%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERunning%20The%20Government%20From%20Jail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20claim%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20first%20chief%20minister%20to%20resign%20after%20bail%20may%20make%20for%20good%20TV%20debates%20but%20is%20not%20grounded%20in%20historical%20context.%20It%20has%20been%20an%20unwritten%20norm%20for%20a%20chief%20minister%20facing%20imminent%20arrest%20to%20resign%20and%20transfer%20responsibilities.%20Examples%20include%20Lalu%20Yadav%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jayalalithaa%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20Jharkhand.%20However%2C%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20presents%20himself%20as%20a%20crusader%20against%20corruption%2C%20chose%20not%20to%20resign%20and%20continued%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20exploiting%20the%20legal%20ambiguities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20explicitly%20ask%20him%20to%20resign%2C%20as%20no%20such%20law%20exists%2C%20but%20their%20bail%20order%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20his%20position%20as%20chief%20minister%20was%20untenable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20and%20subsequent%20judicial%20custody%2C%20AAP%20leaders%20claimed%20he%20could%20run%20the%20Delhi%20government%20from%20jail.%20Delhi's%20Cabinet%20Minister%20Atishi%20Marlena%20even%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20a%20directive%20from%20Kejriwal%20regarding%20water%20and%20sewage%20issues.%20However%2C%20this%20claim%20was%20proven%20false%2C%20as%20Kejriwal%20could%20not%20effectively%20manage%20the%20government%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20any%20student%20of%20politics%20would%20understand%20that%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20rulings%20on%20Article%20356%20and%20defection%20have%20made%20legal%20scrutiny%20rigorous.%20Additionally%2C%20destabilising%20a%20government%20is%20only%20feasible%20with%20a%20thin%20majority%20and%20significant%20internal%20party%20divisions.%20The%20AAP%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20all%20have%20substantial%20majorities%2C%20making%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20rival%20political%20formations%20to%20engineer%20defections%20and%20destabilise%20these%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kejriwal%20thrives%20on%20victimhood%20politics%2C%20using%20it%20as%20a%20strategy%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726488960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fsites%2F3%2F2019%2F10%2F04163431%2Farvind-kejriwal-banega-swasth-india.jpg%22%2C%22orig