%20ethics%20and%20communication%20module).%20This%20is%20a%20community-oriented%20curriculum%20with%20family%20adoption%20programmes%20in%20rural%20setups%20of%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20in%20society%20is%20left%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%2030%20laboratories%20%E2%80%94%20for%20micro-anatomy%2C%20histopathology%2C%20bacteriology%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20the%20college%20is%20equipped%20with%20everything%20a%20medical%20student%20would%20need.%20On%20most%20days%2C%20Zavi%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20anatomy%20lab%2C%20brushing%20up%20on%20the%20names%20of%20the%20different%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20experience%20at%20the%20college%20has%20been%20really%20great%20so%20far.%20I%20learn%20so%20much%20and%20am%20given%20so%20many%20opportunities.%20The%20facilities%20have%20helped%20me%20understand%20concepts%20better.%20I%20know%20of%20youth%20who%20are%20working%20hard%20day%20and%20night%20to%20get%20into%20this%20college%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20step%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351914%2Forgan-donation-in-india-donor-mohan-foundation-dr-sunil-shroff-kbc-episode-kidney-transplant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencouraging%20the%20future%20doctors%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Nagaland%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20opinion%20was%20seconded%20by%20Ritu%20Thurr%2C%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20former%20principal%20director%20for%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%2C%20who%20mentioned%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20he%20anticipated%20that%20young%20doctors%20from%20NIMSR%20would%20enhance%20tertiary-level%20care%20within%20the%20state%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20patients%20to%20seek%20specialised%20medical%20services%20in%20places%20like%20Assam%20or%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20takes%20pride%20in%20speaking%20about%20the%20state-of-the-art%20facilities%20at%20the%20college.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20four%20lecture%20theatres%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F105260%2Findia-literacy-project-interactive-learning-rural-government-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20central%20library%20building%20that%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20a%20330-bed%20hospital%20(which%20will%20be%20extended%20to%20530%20in%20the%20coming%20months)%2C%20an%20upcoming%2014-storey%20building%20that%20is%20set%20to%20be%20constructed%20by%20the%20Japan%20International%20Cooperation%20Agency%20(JICA)%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20have%20a%20private%20helipad%20and%20drone%20area%2C%20staff%20quarters%2C%20dining%20halls%2C%20a%20hostel%20that%20can%20accommodate%20250%20students%2C%20and%20a%20sports%20complex.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Soumya%E2%80%99s%20claims%20have%20confirmed%20that%20the%20120-acre%20land%20is%20brimming%20with%20potential.%20The%20academician%20and%20doctor%20has%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20those%20who%20consider%20setting%20up%20a%20medical%20college%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20job.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20needs%20an%20extreme%20amount%20of%20dedication%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20NIMSR%20will%20grow%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20pausing%20for%20a%20second%2C%20she%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprised%20if%20it%20becomes%20one%20of%20the%20best%20medical%20colleges.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Dr%20Soumya%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fground-reports%2Fnagalands-no-longer-the-only-state-wi