adequate%20to%20meet%20the%20growing%20demands%20of%20the%20population%20and%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrinking%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Chorol%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20existing%20facilities%20are%20ageing%20and%20lack%20the%20capacity%20to%20treat%20the%20increasing%20volume%20of%20wastewater%20generated%20in%20the%20city.%20Significant%20investments%20are%20required%20to%20upgrade%20and%20expand%20the%20water%20treatment%20infrastructure%20in%20Leh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20steps%20include%20upgrading%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288976%2Fsewage-treatment-plant-in-delhi-recycles-wastewater-without-foul-smell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESewage%20Treatment%20Plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20(STPs)%20and%20constructing%20new%20ones%20in%20areas%20currently%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20sewage%20network.%20Authorities%20must%20also%20invest%20in%20advanced%20water%20treatment%20technologies%2C%20such%20as%20membrane%20filtration%2C%20to%20ensure%20treated%20water%20meets%20prescribed%20standards%20for%20safe%20consumption%20and%20environmental%20discharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20need%20to%20expand%20the%20sewage%20collection%20network%20to%20cover%20all%20households%20and%20establishments%20in%20Leh.%20Also%2C%20we%20need%20to%20establish%20a%20regular%20water%20quality%20monitoring%20programme%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20treated%20water%20meets%20the%20prescribed%20standards%20and%20to%20promptly%20identify%20any%20potential%20contamination%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20investment%20required%20to%20take%20all%20these%20measu