g%20a%20piece%20of%20their%20culinary%20prowess%20to%20Kozhikode%E2%80%99s%20Zamorin%20(monarch).%20And%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20the%20cut.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20spice%20trade%20and%20eventually%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20been%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20a%20simple%20blend%20of%20water%2C%20sugar%2C%20corn%20starch%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20citrus%20salt%2C%20and%20flavourings%20birthed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281110%2Fmithai-map-of-india-10-lesser-known-indian-sweets-you-must-try-at-least-once%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dessert%20so%20exquisite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20successor%20dessert%20could%20compete%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20no%20two%20blocks%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20same%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20each%20ingredient%20varies%20from%20proprietor%20to%20proprietor%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20tourists%20and%20locals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20picky%20about%20these%20changing%20nuances%20so%20long%20as%20they%20get%20their%20fill%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20combo%20box%2C%20that%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20combos%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20was%20the%20case%20with%20four%20childhood%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%2C%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%2C%20and%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K.%20Growing%20up%2C%20they%20gorged%20on%20the%20sweet%20treat.%20They%20considered%20it%20a%20usual%20feast.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20they%20moved%20out%20of%20their%20hometown%20to%20study%2C%20that%20they%20realised%20they%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20in%20different%20colleges%20in%20Kerala%2C%20were%20berated%20with%20similar%20requests%20on%20each%20trip%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEnikk%20kurach%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%20venam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Get%20me%20some%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa)%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20came%20from%20teachers%2C%20friends%20and%20hostel%20mates.%20And%20so%20on%20every%20return%20trip%2C%20the%20boys%20would%20return%20loaded%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F210948%2Ffood-history-origin-of-halwa-ceremony-budget-indian-desserts-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolourful%20squares%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20were%20relished%20by%20its%20patrons.%20One%20day%2C%20the%20pattern%20was%20discussed%20over%20some%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20biscuits.%20They%20realised%20that%20people%20beyond%20Kozhikode%20and%20Kerala%20found%20profound%20delight%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conversation%20furthered%2C%20it%20dawned%20on%20the%20four%20that%20while%20each%20had%20grown%20up%20eating%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20preference%20for%20flavour%20differed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20there%20are%20so%20many%20flavours%20that%20existed!%E2%80%9D%20Sanu%20adds.%20And%20this%20sparked%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20be%20an%20umbrella%20of%20sorts%20for%20the%20different%20varieties%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20a%20childhood%20treat%20into%20a%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Kozhikode%2C%20I%20encourage%20you%20to%20take%20a%20walk%20down%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMittaiteruvu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Sweet%20Street).%20Also%20known%20as%20SM%20Street%20(SM%20stands%20for%20sweetmeat)%2C%20the%20lane%20is%20lined%20with%20shop%20upon%20shop%2C%20a%20never-ending%20blur%20of%20colour.%20Look%20closely%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20the%20colour%20is%20lent%20by%20stacks%20of%20coloured%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Esquares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20street%20inception%20dates%20back%20to%20when%20the%20land%20was%20being%20ruled%20by%20the%20Zamorin.%20The%20ruler%20invited%20Gujarati%20sweetmeat%20makers%20to%20set%20up%20shop%20in%20the%20city.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20Box%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehalwas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20every%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20friends%20fortified%20the%20idea%20of%20Fulva%2C%20they%20say%20nostalgia%20was%20a%20main%20ingredient.%20Thesreef%20pitches%20in%20here%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20if%20anyone%20in%20my%20family%20was%20going%20abroad%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20always%20bought%20to%20take%20along%20was%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20grew%20up%20with%20it%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337104%2Feasy-recipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20flavours%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20always%20made%20us%20huge%20fans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Irfan%20interjects%20here%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20in%20the%20market%20for%20the%20last%20500%20years%2C%20there%20is%20still%20no%20established%20brand%20for%20it%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20many%20traditional%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20four%20friends%20at%20a%20Fulva%20pop-up%20store.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364552%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20friends%20are%20attempting%20to%20tap%20into%20sentiments%20linked%20to%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%20shared%20by%20the%20natives%20of%20Kerala%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFulva%20is%20looking%20to%20fill%20these%20gaps.%20The%20startup%20is%20looking%20to%20elevate%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20being%20a%20product%20that%20lies%20on%20a%20bakery%20shelf%20for%20hours%20before%20a%20customer%20walks%20in%20and%20decides%20to%20buy%20it%2C%20to%20a%20product%20of%20prestige%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20it%20its%20rightful%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20venture%20started%20as%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20the%20boys%20now%20spearhead%20it%20full-time.%20Recalling%20their%20first%20package%2C%20Sanu%20shares%20it%20was%20a%20box%20with%2024%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Evarieties.%20Going%20beyond%20the%20usual%20red%20and%20green%20flavours%2C%20there%20was%20also%20an%20experimental%20dry%20coconut%2C%20green%20chilli%2C%20watermelon%2C%20kiwi%2C%20carrot%2C%20pomegranate%2C%20and%20passion%20fruit%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20who%20prepared%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20who%20know%20best%20how%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanu%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%2C%20while%20debating%20on%20whether%20they%20should%20set%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20decided%20to%20task%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwais%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sweet%20makers)%20with%20this.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20the%20product%20more%20authentic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanu%20explains%20adding%20that%20they%20possess%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359191%2Fparsi-food-in-mumbai-cloud-kitchen-farida-nanavaty-karrylicious-dhansak-laga-nu-custard-prawn-patia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20generational%20skill%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20making%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FXpgr5MyMWYM%3Fsi%3Dd_VPY6_6M7WYcryi%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3